abstract: Attacks yesterday on two oil carriers in the Gulf of Oman have stoked fears about tensions between the U.S. and Iran. Petroleum prices could keep climbing.

headline_main: DealBook Briefing: Ganging Up on Big Tech

abstract: Corrections appearing in print on Tuesday, June 11, 2019.
snippet: Corrections appearing in print on Tuesday, June 11, 2019.

abstract: Uniting the aerospace unit of United Technologies and Raytheon will create a huge maker of jet engines and missiles — and could force more mergers in the industry.
